OL,3,CFamily weeps as boy found guilty of
OL,4,Cmurdering teenager Alfie Lewis
OL,6,FA 15-year-old boy has been found
OL,7,Fguilty of murdering teenager Alfie
OL,8,FLewis in
OL,10,FThe boy showed no emotion as the
OL,11,Fverdict was read out at Leeds Crown
OL,12,FCourt after a two week trial.
OL,14,FAlfie, who was 15, was stabbed in the
OL,15,Fstreet in front of pupils, parents and
OL,16,Fteachers from two schools which were
OL,17,Ffinishing for the day in the Horsforth
OL,18,Farea of the city on 7 November last
OL,19,Fyear.
