OL,3,CFamily weeps as boy found guilty of
OL,4,Cmurdering teenager Alfie Lewis
OL,6,FAs the verdict was delivered, friends
OL,7,Fand family of Alfie in the public
OL,8,Fgallery wept and shouted "yes".
OL,10,FMany have been in court throughout the
OL,11,Ftrial wearing T-shirts in Alfie's
OL,12,Ffavourite colour, orange, some bearing
OL,13,Fhis photograph.
OL,15,FThe trial heard how the defendant, who
OL,16,Fwas 14 at the time of the attack and
OL,17,Fcan not be named because of his age,
OL,18,Fstabbed Alfie through the heart at the
OL,19,Fjunction of Church Road and Church
OL,20,FLane as Alfie went to meet friends
OL,21,Fafter school.
