OL,3,CFamily weeps as boy found guilty of
OL,4,Cmurdering teenager Alfie Lewis
OL,6,FWitnesses included several children.
OL,7,FThe youngest to give evidence was 12
OL,8,Fyears-old.
OL,10,FSpeaking outside court after the
OL,11,Fverdict, Alfie's brother Antony Lewis
OL,12,Fthanked witnesses who tried to help
OL,13,FAlfie at the scene of the attack. He
OL,14,Falso paid tribute to everyone involved
OL,15,Fin the investigation and successful
OL,16,Fprosecution.
OL,18,FHe added: "The only justice we would
OL,19,Fwant is for Alfie to come home, to his
OL,20,Fmum and brother, and to us.
