OL,3,CFamily weeps as boy found guilty of
OL,4,Cmurdering teenager Alfie Lewis
OL,6,F"Most of all we would like to say
OL,7,Fthank you to our Alfie, for giving us
OL,8,Fall your love, joy, and humour and
OL,9,Fmaking us smile every day in the 15
OL,10,Fyears we had to enjoy and love you.
OL,12,F"You are always in our hearts and our
OL,13,Fminds, and until we are all together
OL,14,Fagain keep dancing in the sky our
OL,15,Fbeautiful boy. We miss you and we love
OL,16,Fyou, always."
