OL,3,CFamily weeps as boy found guilty of
OL,4,Cmurdering teenager Alfie Lewis
OL,6,FSenior investigator Det Ch Insp Stacey
OL,7,FAtkinson said Alfie was not involved
OL,8,Fin "gangs or any other criminality
OL,9,Fthat could have put him at risk of
OL,10,Fknife crime".
OL,12,F"He had simply gone to meet his
OL,13,Ffriends from school and was not
OL,14,Flooking for a confrontation with
OL,15,Fanyone," she said.
OL,17,FShe said the killer had "planned and
OL,18,Fprepared" the attack, taking a kitchen
OL,19,Fknife from home and waiting until the
OL,20,Fend of the school day.
