OL,3,CFamily weeps as boy found guilty of
OL,4,Cmurdering teenager Alfie Lewis
OL,6,FShe added: "He claimed that he had
OL,7,Facted in self-defence, but the
OL,8,Fevidence from multiple eyewitnesses
OL,9,Fhas shown that he was the aggressor
OL,10,Fwho launched a deliberate and
OL,11,Fdetermined attack repeatedly stabbing
OL,12,FAlfie, who was completely defenceless,
OL,13,Fleaving him fatally wounded.
OL,15,F"We have heard evidence of previous
OL,16,Fincidents involving Alfie and the
OL,17,Fyouth but these were very minor in
OL,18,Fnature. Clearly there is nothing that
OL,19,Fcould justify the murderous violence
OL,20,Fhe used to end Alfie's young life.
