OL,3,CFamily weeps as boy found guilty of
OL,4,Cmurdering teenager Alfie Lewis
OL,6,F"Alfie's murder occurred in a busy
OL,7,Fstreet at school home time and was
OL,8,Fwitnessed by several children and
OL,9,Fpassing members of the public.
OL,10,FUnderstandably, it caused a huge
OL,11,Famount of shock and concern in the
OL,12,Flocal community.
OL,14,F"It is a tragedy that illustrates the
OL,15,Fappalling consequences of knife crime,
OL,16,Fand we can only hope it will hit home
OL,17,Fto young people that it can never be
OL,18,Fright to carry a knife or use violence
OL,19,Fto settle your differences."
OL,21,FSentencing will take place on 21 June.
